{"id":544945,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/益生益事-谷歌推出新服务，让中国人看到了一张/","date":"2016-11-19T18:01:49Z","modified":"2016-11-19T18:01:49Z","title":"益生益事 | 谷歌推出新服务，让中国人看到了一张悲伤的地图","content":"<p>微信号：益生益事（yisheng999yishi）</p>\n<p>谷歌公司上周推出了一个全新的交互式地图——“全球森林监察(GlobalForestWatch)”，它可以实时显示全球森林的覆盖情况。该幅地图的数据来源有多个，其中包括了NASA的森林面积覆盖率的分析数据。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.52.49.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-52-49\" width=\"599\" height=\"349\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544946\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.52.49.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.52.49-300x175.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.52.49-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>这真是一幅令中国人悲伤的地图，现在我们来看看它是怎样的悲伤法。</p>\n<p>最深的绿色表示覆盖率在75%-100%，次深的绿色是50-75%，浅绿是25-50%（如下图示）。灰色的表示覆盖率低于25%。粉色的部分，表示树木正在减少。</p>\n<p>这是亚欧两洲的森林覆盖地图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.53.49.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-53-49\" width=\"598\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544947\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.53.49.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.53.49-300x152.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>现在我们拉近一点，看看中国和周边：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.54.33.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-54-33\" width=\"598\" height=\"384\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544948\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.54.33.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.54.33-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>我们被包围了！</p>\n<p>现在再拉近一点，看看华北华东地区：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.05.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-55-05\" width=\"598\" height=\"287\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544949\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.05.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.05-300x144.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>好吧，有一点点绿。</p>\n<p>再拉近，北京附近：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.37.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-55-37\" width=\"600\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544950\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.37.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.55.37-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>而韩国首尔附近是这样的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.10.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-56-10\" width=\"599\" height=\"676\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544951\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.10.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.10-266x300.png 266w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>日本东京附近是这样的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.35.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-56-35\" width=\"598\" height=\"544\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544952\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.35.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.35-300x273.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>这里是北京：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.57.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-56-57\" width=\"599\" height=\"435\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544953\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.57.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.56.57-300x218.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>这里是首尔：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.57.28.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-57-28\" width=\"599\" height=\"348\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544954\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.57.28.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.57.28-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>这里是东京：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.01.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-58-01\" width=\"599\" height=\"528\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544955\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.01.png 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.01-300x264.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>NASA从太空拍摄雾霾笼罩下的中国：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.26.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-58-26\" width=\"598\" height=\"399\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544956\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.26.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.26-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>谷歌卫星图俯瞰中国大片黄土：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.45.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-58-45\" width=\"597\" height=\"426\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544957\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.45.png 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.58.45-300x214.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" /></p>\n<p>俄罗斯一片翠绿：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.08.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-59-08\" width=\"600\" height=\"599\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544958\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.08.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.08-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.08-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.08-70x70.png 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>中国的环境污染问题：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.44.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-59-44\" width=\"598\" height=\"399\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544959\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.44.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.44-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.37.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-19-at-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%889-59-37\" width=\"598\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544960\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.37.png 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-19-at-上午9.59.37-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>面对绿色植被的不断减少和日趋严重的环境污染，我们的国家和企业应该何去何从，是继续从事环境换取利润，用短期的经济增长来透支子孙后代的幸福，这是需要我们全社会共同关注和努力的方向。</p>\n<p>文章转自 政经参考</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[16932,20002,23711,8615,10193]}